TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {77614=The Raiders marched 88 yards on 15 plays as McFadden concluded Oakland's opening drive with a four-yard touchdown run. McFadden totaled 50 yards on seven carries on the possession which took 7:48 off the clock., 76997=Mohamed Massaquoi hauled in a 12-yard score from McCoy with 1:06 to play to make it a 24-17 game., 78971=Cribbs' 31-yard punt return to the Oakland 42 set up Cleveland's next score.
